snippet.textDisplay: After the epic masterpieces like 'Deora' and 'Kotha Koiyo Na', the expectation from Coke Studio Bangla has become really really high. This may be a good song. But sorry couldn't meet the current standards of Coke Studio Bangla. It was too funky, had too many elements. So the focus shifted continuously. It wasn't possible to enjoy this in a peaceful mind. So this didn't meet my expectations. I would really want Coke Studio Bangla to create more magics like the last two songs. And please avoid exaggeration and excessive inclusion.
